README for Config::IniFile::Subst 1.0.1


=head1 NAME

Config::IniFile::Subst - Flexible processing of INI files with substitution of variables


=head1 SYNOPSIS

  use Config::IniFile::Subst;
  $ini = Config::IniFile::Subst->new(@inifiles);
  $ini->read(@inifiles);
  $ini->get($key, $default);
  $ini->add($key, $value);
  $ini->set($key, $value);
  $ini->delete($key);
  $ini->keys($section);
  $ini->sections();
  $ini->write($file, @comment);


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

This module has external dependencies on the following modules:

 Carp
 File::Spec
 IO::File
 IO::Handle
 version

This module needs for building:

 Test::More
 Test::Pod
 Test::Pod::Coverage

=head1 INSTALLATION

 perl Makefile.PL
 make
 make test

and if all goes well

 make install


